X83 -> Xcard script(MIDI program 59)
X85 -> Xcard script(MIDI program 61)
X86 -> Xcard script(MIDI program 62)
X87 -> Xcard script(MIDI program 63)
I42 -> Internal script(MIDI program 26)
I62 -> Internal script(MIDI program 42)
I66 -> Internal script(MIDI program 46)
C13 -> Internal script(MIDI program 67)
